# Integrations — Landing Page

## Google Analytics 4
- Measurement ID: NEXT_PUBLIC_GA_ID env var
- Events to track: page_view, view_item, add_to_cart, begin_checkout, purchase
- Implement via gtag() in layout.tsx with next/script

## WhatsApp Integration
- Number: +591 76020369 (NEXT_PUBLIC_WHATSAPP_NUMBER)
- Post-purchase message template:
  "Hola! Realicé un pedido #[ORDER_ID] por Bs [TOTAL]. Ya realicé el pago por QR. ¿Pueden confirmar?"
- Floating WhatsApp button: always visible bottom-right on mobile

## Resend (Order Emails)
- Customer email: order confirmation with items + total
- Admin email: new order notification to Aldrin
- Triggered from: checkout Step 2 (when order is created in Supabase)

## Yolo Pago (QR Payment)
- Static QR image: /public/qr-yolo-pago.png
- No API integration needed — manual verification by admin
- Show in Step 2 of CheckoutModal
